  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Please note some restaurants are seasonal and are often open on specific days of the week. Where applicable, half board evening meals include 3 courses (appetizer, main and dessert) and non-alcoholic drinks. Buffet and à la carte breakfast options are available in select restaurants to those who prebook. Alcohol and specialty coffees are not included. Dinner reservations are recommended and strongly advised to be made a few months in advance of the festive period.</p>
<p><strong>Poppy Brasserie </strong>is a casual family restaurant open for breakfast. If you have prebooked breakfast or half board, you'll enjoy your buffet or à la carte breakfast here. The gourmet spread and impressive lake views will be all the fuel you need to set you up nicely for the day ahead.</p>
<p><strong>The Walliser Stube </strong>invites guests to try its innovative European cuisine featuring a variety of classic Swiss, German and regional Alpine dishes. You'll also find an impressive line-up of Alpine beer and classic cocktails. The floor to ceiling wine library also houses more than 500 bottles to choose from!</p>
<p><strong>Lakeview Lounge</strong> is an iconic and elegant restaurant come bar with spectacular, world-class views over Lake Louise and Victoria Glacier. Seasonal inspired menus and an extensive wine and cocktail list are on offer here.</p>
<p><strong>Fairview Bar &amp; Restaurant </strong>offers vibrant signature dishes, distinctive cocktails and everything in between. The art-deco styled space looks over the lake and Fairview's namesake peak.</p>
<p><strong>Alpine Social </strong>is the perfect hub for hearty comfort food that will satisfy your mountain-size appetite. Head here to meet, eat and celebrate in a warm and friendly environment. </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
