  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Fairmont Rooms</strong> sleep one or two people in a king or two twin beds. Rooms overlook the Chateau grounds and hillside.</p>
<p><strong>Lakeview Fairmont Rooms</strong> with spectacular views of the frozen lake and glacier are available on request. </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Mount Temple Rooms </strong>sleep up to four guests. These are large rooms and have one king or two queen beds and are located in the new wing of the hotel. Rooms overlook the Chateau grounds and hillside.  </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Lakeview Rooms </strong>sleep up to four guests. These spacious rooms have one king or two queen beds. Expect spectacular views of the frozen lake and glacier. </p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> and <strong>Gold Floor</strong> rooms are available on request, call for more information. </p>
